187
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije se bilo u kontaktima s njima.

188
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tu gradski fakirin.

189
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali glede ti ljudi su koji to vole.

190
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji žive, koji će doći, koji će podržati manifestaciju.

191
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da im se i grad pomogne s nekim sitnim donacijama ili bilo šta za njihove kudova.

192
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su nosioci koji imaju puno članova.

193
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji mogu odraditi neke stvari.

194
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] To bi ispalo ko da u rijeci tamo odrekne se rijeka zvončara.

195
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vidio da je tom grad i to bila čast.

196
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je čast i...

197
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da je ono kužiš.

198
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je prekrasno.

199
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] A stvarno je doživlja.

200
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo je bučno.

201
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Velim je.

202
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je doživlja stvarno.

203
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ljudi koji vole to.

204
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ljudi koji ne vole.

205
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[UNKNOWN] Da.

206
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je ono tradicija.

207
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa isto pozivam.

208
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kada sam bio Hellboy.

209
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekao ne morate doći ni maskiran.

210
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam znao normalno svoju masku kad sam otkrije.

211
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se malo u čudu nagledao.

212
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treba i bradu skidati i sve.

213
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim da nosim bradu već osam godina.

214
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ha lajde prisutno mi je to.

215
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I stvarno smo ljude pozivali.

216
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Medijski sam bio popraćen.

217
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:39,000
