225
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, ako ti ja to gledam, to je nekakva sputanost.

226
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nešto smo, znaš, malo ovo ono.

227
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ono, da je Hellboy bio u Zagrebu?

228
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,000
