229
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došlo bi.

230
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi da si ti ko Hellboy bio.

231
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to ti mene smeta.

232
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta podrška kad se neko trudne nešto da ga se ne podrži.

233
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,000
