234
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tog svjestan.

235
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne dobro.

236
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne dobro.

237
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne dobro.

238
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne veze, ali treba ustrajat.

239
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tak, da.

240
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Toma, negde sam počital da nisi baš ljubitelj ovog karnevala Rio de Janeiro.

241
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, to je nešto drugo.

242
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jel?

243
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ljubitelj Hellwina, evo.

244
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Aha.

245
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] O, dobro, to nisam ni ja.

246
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

247
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nisam ljubitelj, evo ne.

248
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:39,000
