269
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I da ih ne možeš...

270
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj da si malo vode popiče, vama sam mi se osušao.

271
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,000
