274
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Običaje.

275
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Lijepo ih je vidjeti isto.

276
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo manifestacije te koje...

277
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Logički mi je da ih se zove i da njegujemo te maškare.

278
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
