284
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta imamo s njima?

285
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemamo, nemamo.

286
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš nemamo ništa.

287
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je to malo...

288
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da mi žalosno...

289
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali smo mi povodljivi.

290
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Al povodljivi smo.

291
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je došlo da me krivo ne strate sa zapada i sad to valja.

292
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ha, ne znači da valja.

293
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gle, ne znači da valja.

294
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] A opet...

295
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, gledaj, možda se jednog dana vrati.

296
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se trudimo, trudimo pa ćemo vidjeti.

297
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je helovina ovo.

298
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gle, a ovo...

299
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krića im pitao za Rio dole.

300
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto da opet drugačije.

301
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto sad ne možemo uspoređivati.

302
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Samoboru su fašnike.

303
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

304
