310
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Rijeci ti je...

311
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Alegorijska kola velika se rade i sve.

312
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Samoboru je opet malo drugačiji taj stil.

313
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto se naprave normalno alegorijska kola i to.

314
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali malo drugačije je prezentiranje tih maski.

315
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Rijeci se više pleše.

316
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ovde se i recitira u Samoboru i tako.

317
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali velim, u kontaktima se i sve.

318
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Al...

319
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja velim, ja ovde imam viziju za Karlovac.

320
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] A biti Karlovac nema pravo karnevala.

321
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima ono neki dječji karnevali.

322
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde gledaj, dječja povorka se radi velim.

323
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam opet...

324
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Opet pobornik toga da...

325
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,000
