328
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad bi grad moglo posjediti puno ljudi.

329
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

330
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,000
