332
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, održala se ta dječja povorka.

333
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

334
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, iz pouzdanih izvora djeca izađu iz vrtića Grabrik u 10 i 10.

335
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I djecu vratišu vrtiću Grabrik 20 do 12.

336
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

337
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:38,000
